	<h1>Careers</h1>
	<p>At Tactical Cyber, we believe strong security starts with a strong team. Our work is challenging, practical, and grounded in real-world problem solving, but we are equally committed to maintaining a healthy work-life balance. We offer competitive compensation and benefits, including health coverage, retirement options, and generous paid time off. Team members are supported in their professional growth through tuition reimbursement, certification support, and ongoing training opportunities. Whether working independently or collaborating across engagements, our culture emphasizes discipline, curiosity, and steady, sustainable performance.</p>
