	<summary style="cursor: zoom-in;"><strong>Penetration Tester</strong></summary>
	<p><strong>Tactical Cyber LLC</strong> | Remote / Hybrid (U.S.-based preferred)</p>
    <p><strong>Position Overview</strong></p>
    <img src="/TC_employee.png" alt="A Typical Employee of Tactical Cyber">
    <p>Tactical Cyber is seeking a skilled and motivated Penetration Tester to join our growing cybersecurity team. In this role, you will conduct authorized, controlled security assessments that simulate real-world attacks against client environments.</p>
	<p>You will identify vulnerabilities across networks, systems, and applications, validate their impact through exploitation, and provide clear, actionable reporting to support remediation efforts. This position blends technical execution with client-facing communication, supporting organizations that rely on Tactical Cyber for defensible, practical security outcomes.</p>
	<p>Penetration testers play a proactive role in cybersecurity by simulating attacks to uncover weaknesses before adversaries can exploit them.<p></details>
